<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA25">
<l>toḻutāṟ paḻutuṇṭē tūnī rulaka</l>
<l>muḻutuṇṭu moykuḻalā ḷāycci – viḻutuṇṭa</l>
<l>vāyāṉai mālviṭaiyēḻ ceṟṟāṉai vāṉavarkkuñ</l>
<l>cēyāṉai neñcē ciṟantu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is it a mistake, heart, if you worship exultantly</l>
<l>the one who is distant even for the celestials, the one who destroyed seven huge bulls,</l>
<l>the one with a mouth that ate the butter of the cowherdess, her with dense curls,</l>
<l>after eating the whole of the world [surrounded] by clear water?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
